data.description: You'll love this nearly new two story with panoramic views and stunning sunsets. Enjoy cool summer breezes on the covered front porch or rear deck. This easy living, open floor plan features a library/office and a two story great room with a wall of windows (tinted for energy efficiency). The adjoining eat in kitchen has a center island work space with farm style sink, & bar overhang, granite counter tops, tiled back splash, stainless appliances, gas range and a sunlit breakfast nook. The rear deck has a low maintenance composite decking. The first floor primary suite has a pampering bath with soaking tub, double sink, dressing table area, shower and walk in closet. Want to catch the clutter? The mud room with cubbies is right off the garage. There is a separate laundry room so you More.. don't have to step over the laundry when coming into the house from the garage. The second level features a multi-functional loft area, 2 bedrooms and a full bath. The lower level is a blank canvas waiting for you to customize as you like. There are full sized windows and rough ins for a bath. Conveniently located minutes from LaGrange where you'll find dining, shopping, medical facilities and easy access to I71. Visit today! You won't be disappointed. Beth Rojas with Agency title is facilitating the short sale. We request that closing take place at Agency Title.
